msg: QPID-2059 : CI failures were due to threading races to exhaust prefetch before delivered messages could be acked. So adjusted test to have the client dispatcher ready to deliver and relax the constraint that we validate which actor is doing the logging. The fact the state has changed correctly is the important factor.
